Set the start command to "python manage.py migrate && gunicorn traffic_web.wsgi:application --bind 0.0.0.0:${PORT:-8000}" to fix this build failure. Railpack detected Python but could not auto-detect this as a Django project because requirements.txt includes multiple web frameworks (Django, FastAPI, Streamlit). The empty Procfile provided no fallback, so a start command must be set explicitly.